rows.label: qst201211_msg0003
rows.name:
We did! Well? Don't
they look delicious?

rows.label: qst201211_msg0004
rows.name:
Even I can make simple things
like cookies, you know!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0005
rows.name:
It would have been easier if you didn't
insist on eyeballing the measurements
and dumping everything in at once.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey! You promised you
wouldn't say anything!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0008
rows.name:
Well, since you're here,
you should try one.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0012
rows.name:
Don't! When you say it, it
doesn't sound like a joke!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0014
rows.name:
Relax, they're not
poisoned. Go on, try one!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0019
rows.name:
Delicious! This is
just how I like them!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0021
rows.name:
Yes! Did you hear that,
Seori? Acceptable! Not
bad for a first try, eh?

rows.label: qst201211_msg0022
rows.name:
...You'll never improve if
you're satisfied with that.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0023
rows.name:
Aw, c'mon. I'm the type who
grows with praise, you know.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0025
rows.name:
Anyway, we've got their
approval. Let's go hand
out the Whelzaman Cookies.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0026
rows.name:
Right. Let's give them to
the kids of Fons Maim.
